Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:49.92,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.96,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.30,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:03.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's four in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:06.09,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,The early bird catches the worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:07.63,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Not only do you have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your regular duties at \Nthe inn to take care of,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:12.53,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,you also have to help with the \Npreparations for our wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:15.58,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I've concluded that \Ncutting the sleeping time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of you young ones, will be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the first step to making this a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.89,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:24.62,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you now have a meeting \Nwith Enishing you must attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.32,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, to the staff dining room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:35.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Takako's \Nso fired up suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 22\NA Determined One-Sided Crush
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.62,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Ms. Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:54.86,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin a wonderful day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:57.01,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:59.01,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.74,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, have a seat like \Neveryone else, Ms. Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.59,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll now begin the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.95,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.62,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:13.63,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what led Ryunosuke \NAkutagawa to write {\i1}Rashomon{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.37,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,His wedding with Yayoi Yoshida,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a girl he'd known since he \Nwas a child, had been called off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.96,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:25.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It never rings, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:27.81,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What about \N your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.65,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not a good time \Nto bring up stuff like-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.26,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:45.04,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you called \Nme in the middle of class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.33,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:50.33,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I just have this image of \Nyou constantly at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.51,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that you're \Na high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.25,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I received an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enishi's getting married, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:05.30,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? You're busy with work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a lot to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:10.74,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send him a congratulatory \Nmessage, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:13.19,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Enishi, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,He's streaked ahead of you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:17.98,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:23.95,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your relationships with your \Nboyfriends last too long, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:28.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean to you when \Nyou go out with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:32.22,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? You've gone and caught \Nyourself another boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.59,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hmm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:40.13,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe it's because I still have a \None-sided crush on your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:42.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A one-sided crush?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.74,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to scream at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.85,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I said something \Nnice for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.95,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A one-sided crush?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect those words
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from my sex crazed mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:57.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.29,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to find a new love because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't forget my old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.85,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't get anything out of that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, it's been 15 years \Nsince your father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.41,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I've been thinking that maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to get anything out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:15.82,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:19.78,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's once in a lifetime that you \Nmeet someone you love so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the fact that I met him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was lucky in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:25.56,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:26.59,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.39,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hearing her talk about \Nher one-sided crush made
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my heart beat so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,One-sided crush?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.35,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did I try to forget about Ko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:03.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Minchi is so serious about Tohru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:15.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did I think I couldn't have \Na one-sided crush on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Home Economics Room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.78,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.78,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:29.76,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad for an amateur's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.40,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is for \Nsomeone to try it on,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can make some minor adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Could you try it on, Yuina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.22,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.56,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that putting on a wedding dress
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,delays your marriage in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:43.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,If I tried it, I'd be \Ndragging the bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:58.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like this is déjà vu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:01.81,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Not a pleasant déjà vu either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.17,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I take this off now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:05.55,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:09.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoe is doing our share of the \Nduties at the inn right now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.36,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we should ask Tsurugi to try it on, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.58,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,She may not be as...\Nbig as Takako there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.32,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,but as long as hers aren't \Nbigger, she can try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:21.91,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,As long as hers aren't bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:22.52,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.46,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're done for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:28.21,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to start practicing \Nmaking the dishes for the party now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:29.55,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.56,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of have an idea, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:34.68,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Minko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.72,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.98,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:45.52,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:48.91,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I've decided \Nto stop spoiling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:49.58,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.91,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed that you have to be hard \Non them when they're in a slump,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order for them to overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.58,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how you were \Nruthless with me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.81,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ruth... less?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.17,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi sure is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:07.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.38,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.82,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,We all made this together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are some minor \Nadjustments we need to make, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.56,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,No, I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:18.22,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.01,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I hate wearing things with frills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.10,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, Minchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.45,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.52,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.50,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind that you dislike me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:40.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,but we made that dress
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,together with Yuina for Takako and \Nthe young master's wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,We worked really hard on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,How could you-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.22,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:50.80,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,"Worked really hard"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.68,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,So has Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:57.84,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,But you stepped all over \Nhis feelings for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.06,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What? T-Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:05.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've decided that I have a \None-sided crush on Ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be direct \Nlike you, Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.23,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.45,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.41,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have a crush?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:17.87,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Just go out with Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.68,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:20.52,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, I won't be able \Nto go out with anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.83,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I've already decided \Nthat I have a crush on Ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.96,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.69,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.32,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,He's just some loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:31.80,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,M-Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You've never even seen him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:38.05,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone's a loser compared to Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:38.05,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:42.01,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru's so handsome! He's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.19,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:51.52,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Minko, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.48,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you? Stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.31,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:36.53,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you're right. \NI'm kind of interested in Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:41.33,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I do like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:44.85,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like I \Nwant to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:48.15,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I just get excited watching her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.74,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,trying to imagine what kind \Nof crazy stunt she'll pull next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:58.97,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, you \Nkeep me in great suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:02.99,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:05.40,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did I just say something awful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.81,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,No... No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:09.66,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:18.53,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You're willing to watch over \Nme without even liking me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:28.13,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You really are stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.88,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I've got most of the dirt off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.01,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.60,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:43.98,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I was really moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:50.10,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been in love before,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:53.02,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought what you \Nsaid was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.77,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about continuing your crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:05.30,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting isn't nice, but I \Nthink both of you are wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:08.62,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,You're both able to \Nlove someone so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.54,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nakochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.75,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "I'm moved"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.59,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.57,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:29.31,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It looks great on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.79,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we should get \Nher to hold some white flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to make it \Nmore appealing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:43.22,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll borrow the flowers by the staircase!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:44.97,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nakochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.04,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Is your nose okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:57.17,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,See-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.18,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.17,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:01.92,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:07.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A-As in you're going to try and\N force me to go out with Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:08.42,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.44,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.96,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go out with him, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.64,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to give that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.55,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go out with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going to continue my crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.40,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:27.43,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be direct \Nlike you said, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:34.01,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Balut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:40.04,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ohana? Did you two fight ag-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,"Balut" is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:50.26,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And after that, the preparations for \Nthe wedding went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.90,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sort of decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:59.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that I'd confess to Ko after the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.15,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.03,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:10.03,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,You decorated in even \Nthe smallest of places!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.87,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I have the \Nfeeling that this will
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.35,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be a wonderful wedding \Nthanks to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.45,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,This is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I think so too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:26.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:37.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're so pretty, Takako...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:39.95,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:44.40,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,This is the day a woman looks \Nthe prettiest in her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.78,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,In a woman's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.63,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:51.78,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,About the bouquet toss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:54.62,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:00.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you since college.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:02.40,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,When did you start dating Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.71,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.55,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We've become bride and \Ngroom on this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:15.32,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,and we're so happy to be able to announce
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this to you all this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:22.90,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We swear to work \Ntogether as a married couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:27.18,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,and to start up a warm, happy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:46.55,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.72,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,The wedding ceremony's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:02.58,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're in a race against time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:03.44,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:12.86,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.29,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nervous about being \Nthe master of ceremonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.20,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Oshimizu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.25,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,does my hair look fine? Is it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:22.86,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,It looks fine! Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:30.88,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oshimizu looks so nice \Nwhen she's hustling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.33,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,A kitchen is a battlefield! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:34.26,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.22,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:37.19,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, give me some orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:37.81,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.43,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You're in charge today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:42.49,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:45.19,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Could you parboil those vegetables,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.44,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,descale the carp,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.44,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,fry those,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.57,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,and decorate the dishes \Nwith the cucumbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.45,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's quite a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:57.32,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'd like to read the \Ncongratulatory greetings now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:01.60,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,This is from the groom's older \Nsister, Satsuki Matsumae.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:05.14,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,"They always say that a relationship \Ngets better after a stormy fight,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:07.52,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,"but I'm not sure what the \Nweather is like today."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:12.85,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,"Either way, you need to make \Nsure she's wet, all right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.26,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.55,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What about the next dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.81,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,The previous one was the last of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:24.02,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Great work today, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Invitations?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:30.28,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,We're invited to the wedding too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You look so pretty, Takako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:35.74,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:41.41,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, these are all so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:45.39,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've tasted \NTohru's cooking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:51.36,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I couldn't stop \Nhim from doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:54.66,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,So, for our next performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.22,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where art thou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:02.95,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where art thou, my destined love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.75,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.89,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved... Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.99,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.86,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for the baiser amor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:19.37,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,W-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:20.51,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,Wait-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.65,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't react, or you'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:50.93,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,On a morning without clocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:58.92,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,two lovers smile and laugh while \Nbeing embraced by the white clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:06.79,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Sunlight shines through a tiny gap,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:14.96,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,and birds are singing freely \Nbeyond the windowsill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:23.02,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Time will extend as long as \Ntheir hands are held tight;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:31.27,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,a short eternity is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:36.43,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't help out with this wedding at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:42.78,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,But these two, and the young workers at Kissuiso,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.05,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,have created such an incredible ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.20,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for boring you \Nwith stories of my past,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:52.26,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,but 40 years ago, I created Kissuiso
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with my late husband, \Nand with Denroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:58.26,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,No, with Mr. Denroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.37,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:04.94,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stumble and get lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you challenge yourself to new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:11.43,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to create something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:17.37,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to seeing \Nthe new things these two,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the rest of Kissuiso create,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:24.95,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,while I'll sit back and enjoy \Nmy tea from the far distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's future?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.81,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Watching from afar?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:27.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It ended without any troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:28.78,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:32.34,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everything's \Njust about cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:35.42,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:40.54,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,about that speech you gave earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:50.85,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why I asked you all here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:56.53,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,is because Mr. Denroku \Ntold me the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:22:58.72,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:01.06,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,that he wanted someone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to succeed the logs he \Nkept for over 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.98,0:23:12.81,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you're \Nquitting Kissuiso, Beanman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.26,0:23:15.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:20.81,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,These logs are like a \Nhistory book of Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:24.54,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,The tears, the laughs... \Neverything is written in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:27.46,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Look how worn it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:34.47,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about sealing \NKissuiso, along with these logs,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:37.29,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,after the Bonbori festival this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.12,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,You going to see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:41.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:42.86,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Your crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:43.56,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:46.89,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,A man is responsible \Nfor waiting patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:49.95,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana, you're nothing \Nlike a bland coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.44,0:23:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 23\NCompensation for the Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
